OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAll parts will have a dry day.
OL,6,FCloud breaking this morning to leave
OL,7,Fsome sunshine for the rest of the day,
OL,8,Fbut may linger along the north coast,
OL,9,Fand spread to the east coast this
OL,10,Fafternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,13,Fcloud spreading inland. Then the rest
OL,14,Fof the night will be dry and cloudy.
OL,15,FClearer across Upper Deeside with a
OL,16,Ffrost.
OL,17,
OL,18,CWednesday:FA dry day. Overnight cloud
OL,19,Fwill gradually lift and break to allow
OL,20,Fsome sunny intervals by afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
