OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,6,Fand settled. Overnight low cloud will
OL,7,Fmostly burn off through the mornings
OL,8,Fbut may linger around coastal
OL,9,Fdistricts. Warm inland, chilly along
OL,10,Fcloudier coasts. Patchy overnight
OL,11,Ffrost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
